      <title>乌克兰在军队中打击赌博成瘾问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/ukraine-tackles-gambling-addiction-within-its-military-ranks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心赌博活动会削弱士气并构成安全风险，乌克兰当局将寻求遏制军队赌博成瘾的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/ukraine-tackles-gambling-addiction-within-its-military-ranks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 13:19:38 GMT</pubDate>
