    <item>
      <title>普京在人力挑战之际在乌克兰策划消耗战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/ukraine-russia-war-putin-gears-up-for-war-of-attrition-amid-manpower-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京决心让乌克兰屈服，并押注自己能够比基辅的西方支持者坚持得更久，并在战场上取得胜利，尽管俄罗斯军队只取得了停滞不前的进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/ukraine-russia-war-putin-gears-up-for-war-of-attrition-amid-manpower-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 13:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
